Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:52.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.91,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
